dct_title_s: Kaart van het noordlyk gedeelte der Verëenigde Staaten van Noord Amerika
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Prime meridian: Paris and Isle de Fer. Appears in Bachiene's Atlas tot opheldering der hedendaagsche historie. Te Amsterdam : M. Schalekamp, 1785. Aanhangzel. A close copy of the French map of Rigobert Bonne entitled Carte de la partie nord, des Etats Unis, de l'Amerique Septentrionale, which was originally published in his Atlas de toutes les parties connues de globe terrestre.
